title: Bump webpack-dev-server from 2.11.5 to 3.1.11

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [webpack-dev-server](https://github.com/webpack/webpack-dev-server) from 2.11.5 to 3.1.11.
